snippet.title: NES Super Lava Bros (Hard) TAS in 5:28.326 (5:25.048 RTA Timing)
snippet.description:
This is the first TAS to beat Kosmic's Most recent ROMHACK in record ASAP!
Also if you hear breathing or someone else like my brother talking, it's because I forgot to turn off the microphone before recording the TAS.
